name: Dickland
description:
Dickland is an exciting pixel 2D platformer with the ability to play together. The main feature is the environment, namely the amazing pussy world with its corresponding inhabitants.

Background:
Once in a kingdom called "Dickland" there was a fascinating story. Evil Assholes from a neighboring state stole several small pisek residents. All the residents of "Dickland" were afraid for the lives of these kids, but of course they began to fear for their lives more, so except for two brave heroes, no one went to save the children. So there was a story about heroes with unremarkable nicknames "The bigger of the little ones" and "Bound in Latex".
